Text:
How do you open this file?  I had to change the .zip to .rar to unarchive the first file, and it left me with Easy.CD-DA.Extractor.10.5.data

What opens the Easy.CD-DA.Extractor.10.5.data file?

Ah, I renamed the .data to .exe and ran it.  It is NOT Easy CD-DA - it is SUPER.  Some freeware app I never heard of.

SUPER ÂŠ (Simplified Universal Player Encoder & Renderer) a GUI to ffmpeg, mencoder, mplayer, x264, ffmpeg2theora and the theora/vorbis RealProducer plugIn. Player and Encoder of various types of multimedia files.
